{"title":"纯净安装Windows10系统","date":"2020-12-21T14:03:35.482Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Dec 21, 2020","L":"12/21/2020","MM-DD":"12-21"},"thumbnail":"https://gitee.com/Qinin/my-image/raw/master/2020/Windows10Wallpapers.jpg","link":"2020/12/21/纯净安装Windows10系统","updated":"2020-12-22T14:02:17.517Z","content":"<h1 id=\"纯净安装windows10系统\">纯净安装Windows10系统<a title=\"#纯净安装windows10系统\" href=\"#纯净安装windows10系统\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"一、下载系统镜像iso\">一、下载系统镜像ISO<a title=\"#一、下载系统镜像iso\" href=\"#一、下载系统镜像iso\"></a></h2>\n<p>百度【我告诉你】选择喜欢的镜像下载即可</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://msdn.itellyou.cn/\" target=\"_blank\">https://msdn.itellyou.cn/</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/Qinin/my-image/raw/master/2020/image-20201221213833700.png\" alt=\"image-20201221213833700\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"二、使用软碟通制作u盘启动盘\">二、使用软碟通制作U盘启动盘<a title=\"#二、使用软碟通制作u盘启动盘\" href=\"#二、使用软碟通制作u盘启动盘\"></a></h2>\n<p>下载页：<a href=\"https://cn.ultraiso.net/xiazai.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://cn.ultraiso.net/xiazai.html</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/Qinin/my-image/raw/master/2020/image-20201221214100727.png\" alt=\"image-20201221214100727\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"三、u盘启动安装镜像\">三、U盘启动安装镜像<a title=\"#三、u盘启动安装镜像\" href=\"#三、u盘启动安装镜像\"></a></h2>\n<p>将制作好的U盘插入电脑，电脑选择U盘启动（del键或者F2、F9键视电脑型号而定），选择UEFI启动U盘</p>\n<h2 id=\"四、纯净安装系统\">四、纯净安装系统<a title=\"#四、纯净安装系统\" href=\"#四、纯净安装系统\"></a></h2>\n<p>1、进入安装界面，按<strong>Shift+F10</strong>进入命令行</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/Qinin/my-image/raw/master/2020/image-20201221215121111.png\" alt=\"image-20201221215121111\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p>2、启动<strong>diskpart</strong>磁盘管理器，并选择安装盘</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/Qinin/my-image/raw/master/2020/image-20201221215328605.png\" alt=\"image-20201221215328605\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p>3、清除磁盘信息，并转换格式为<strong>GPT</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/Qinin/my-image/raw/master/2020/image-20201221215506100.png\" alt=\"image-20201221215506100\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p>4、建立硬盘分区</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/Qinin/my-image/raw/master/2020/image-20201221215612947.png\" alt=\"image-20201221215612947\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><u>到这里，完成了。连续输入两次EXIT，退出命令工具。此步骤EFI和MSR分区可以再大一点，根据你自己的情况定，不过不要超过512M</u></p>\n<p>5、安装系统提示进行下一步安装即可</p>\n","prev":{"title":"跨桌面应用框架","link":"2021/01/05/跨桌面应用框架"},"next":{"title":"Hello World","link":"2020/12/12/hello-world"},"plink":"http://example.com/2020/12/21/纯净安装Windows10系统/","toc":[{"id":"纯净安装windows10系统","title":"纯净安装Windows10系统","index":"1","children":[{"id":"一、下载系统镜像iso","title":"一、下载系统镜像ISO","index":"1.1"},{"id":"二、使用软碟通制作u盘启动盘","title":"二、使用软碟通制作U盘启动盘","index":"1.2"},{"id":"三、u盘启动安装镜像","title":"三、U盘启动安装镜像","index":"1.3"},{"id":"四、纯净安装系统","title":"四、纯净安装系统","index":"1.4"}]}]}